com.customlbs.library.model

Class Building

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.customlbs.library.model.Building
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Building
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable

    Model class representing a building.

    Note: Buildings retrieved with Indoors.getImportedBuildings(ImportedBuildingCallback) or Indoors.getOnlineBuildings(OnlineBuildingCallback) will not be fully initialized with all their members. Floor or tile members will not be set as they are intended to show all available buildings.

    Buildings retrieved from IndoorsLocationListener or via Indoors.getBuilding(Building, LoadingBuildingCallback) will have all their members set.
